EnumFieldVal = enum
  efvNone, efvIdent, efvOrdinal, efvString, efvOrdString
  Source Edit 
RTimeOrdinalKind = enum
  rtokInt, rtokBool, rtokChar
  Source Edit 
RTimeOrdinal = object
  case kind*: RTimeOrdinalKind
  of rtokInt:
      intVal*: BiggestInt

  of rtokBool:
      boolVal*: bool

  of rtokChar:
      charVal*: char
  Source Edit 
EnumField[NNode] = object
  docComment*: string
  codeComment*: string
  name*: string
  value*: Option[NNode]
  declNode*: Option[NNode]
  case kind*: EnumFieldVal
  of efvNone:
      nil

  of efvIdent:
      ident*: NNode

  of efvOrdinal:
      ordVal*: RTimeOrdinal

  of efvString:
      strval*: string

  of efvOrdString:
      ordStr*: tuple[ordVal: RTimeOrdinal, strval: string]
  Source Edit
